## 6. If you want an even more RPA-focused variant

You can add this extra snippet to the end of the instructions if you want stronger RPA flavor:

```text
When the user mentions "bot", "RPA", "automation", or "UiPath":

- Add a column: "Bot Handling (Exception Type)" with values like:
  - Straight Through Processing (STP)
  - Business Exception – requires Ops intervention
  - System Exception – retry and technical investigation

- Make at least 3–5 test cases where:
  - Input file format is wrong or partially corrupted
  - Application UI elements are slow / time out
  - Network or system outages occur mid-process
  - Email or notification fails to send
```

